[SN]TITLE[SN]
Pension payments to increase by 2.1% in Jersey

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Pension payments in Jersey will increase in line with the island's average rise in earnings, the government has announced.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The States confirmed pension payments would go up by 2.1% on 1 October, to match the increase in average weekly earnings over the past year.
